					p Moreover, given my past entrepreneurial experience in building and managing a coworking space, I developed a solid understanding of what building a product means: from design (both in the physical and digital realm) to marketing &amp; sales, pricing, admin, client acquisition, client retention, customer care, and all the daily problem-solving founders are accustomed to.
